om\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4740376-tlt-the-bessent-bottom\" target=\"_blank\">article</a> outlining why.</p> <p>Given</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/118370564/image_118370564.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742659-tltw-bullish-bonds-then-avoid-tltw", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 19:49:32"}, {"id": "4742654", "title": "SPVU: Improved Outlook But This Enhanced Value ETF Isn't The Best Choice", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Wooden seesaw scale empty on wooden sphere on wood table with wording VALUE and PRICE balancing\" data-id=\"1303850380\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"3898px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">marchmeena29</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p><span>I </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4506909-spvu-an-ultra-concentrated-value-etf-you-should-avoid\"><span>last reviewed</span></a><span> the Invesco S&amp;P 500 Enhanced Value ETF (</span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPVU\" title=\"Invesco S&amp;P 500\u00ae Enhanced Value ETF\">SPVU</a></span><span>) on May 5, 2022, recommending readers avoid it due to my concerns about concentration and high risk. Since that review was published, SPVU has lagged behind most</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303850380/image_1303850380.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742654-spvu-improved-outlook-but-this-enhanced-value-etf-isnt-the-best-choice", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 19:34:20"}, {"id": "4742558", "title": "Ladder Capital: 8% Yield And Solid Dividend Coverage Make It A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"8% percentage rate icon on a white background\" data-id=\"476981829\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/476981829/image_476981829.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.